txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Clean tails from the worms surrounding Gabilshathûr. Delivery of the items should be made to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
'Good to know that these things will not bother us any longer.'
'Those worms need to be thinned out. There are simply too many of them.'
The dwarves at Gabilshathûr await a delivery of clean tails to be made to Avar.
Deliver the clean tails to Avar at Gabilshathûr in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver clean tails from the worms surrounding Gabilshathûr to Avar at the dwarf-outpost.
Wanted: Clean tails from the worms surrounding Gabilshathûr.
